      value: 13.6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: greeting
      value: '"Hello, detective. Did you feel the ground shake?"'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: answerOne
      value: Professor Vance? Nothing! I was entirely focused on my acoustic survey.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: answerTwo
      value: I was halfway up the stairs inside the main clock tower when I heard
        glass shatter.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: mainCamera
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 519420031}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: evidenceClock
      value: A broken gear? I study resonant frequencies, detective, not antique
        clock repair
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: evidenceRubbing
      value: A charcoal rubbing of a plaque? What does that have to do with my acoustic
        survey?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: evidenceCasebook
      value: Wait, a 1906 photo of the rubble? ...Fine! The clock tower collapsed
        in the quake. I wasn't up there. I was taking a nap in the choir loft!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8735235304390759350, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 915474098, guid: 7a6100b9600724148af6f713d15c089f, type: 3}
