      value: -2.8
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5263210255893720996, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_AnchoredPosition.y
      value: 3.3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: greeting
      value: Oh, dear. The damage to these historical archives is simply devastating.
        Mind where you step.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: answerOne
      value: Just the Founder's Plaque. A tragedy! It was entirely crushed when the
        east wall collapsed.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: answerTwo
      value: I was outside in the courtyard reading, completely away from the archives.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: mainCamera
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 519420031}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: isTheCulprit
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: evidenceClock
      value: A gear? Perhaps from the tower, but I deal in documents and inscriptions,
        not machinery.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: evidenceRubbing
      value: A fresh charcoal rubbing of the Founder's Plaque? But... I told everyone
        it was destroyed! ...Alright, fine. I hid the plaque myself to protect it
        from scavengers, but I needed the rubbing to translate the inscription!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: winScreenCanvas
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 8264757}
    - target: {fileID: 7660150603591251880, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: evidenceCasebook
      value: A photograph of the rubble? Yes, very sad, but it doesn't help me find
        my missing artifacts.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8735235304390759350, guid: 97d866a41255ff541ab279c1dca83824, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1738075115, guid: d5a7368d8119b294388ac4db4462bf8f, type: 3}
